Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:08.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight won't end until I fulfill my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:14.57,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come to achieve that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:19.86,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years time I'll be living the dream
