Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it can't win.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it can beat \N{\i1}Crow{\i0} and {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With 3 for Win
