Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in our majority vote,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto's {\i1}Perfect Crime Club
