Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Oonishi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't pass Ashirogi here,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.17,0:00:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't be able to draw\N for Jack anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the reason for this vote.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to change my vote!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Change it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it 4 against 3.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Ashirogi passes, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous for us
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to let Ashirogi go based \Non a vote in the first place!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We should take better\N care of our authors!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.37,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a position to \Ninfluence the lives of our authors.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.63,0:01:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a different \Nstory if the vote was 7 to 0,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.35,0:01:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but to abandon our authors\N over such a narrow margin
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,may not be the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heishi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I judged they would lose,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but we should leave this decision to the readers, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast my vote for them to win.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want them to win.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the decision to \Nthe readers, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we've always done.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also change my vote to win.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.02,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0} will be serialized!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the news for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Details will come later!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to celebrating! I'll get the cake!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, it looks like you've got\N yourself a serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll congratulate you, just for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can compete with you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward \Nto your first chapter!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.81,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now our real battle begins.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you that we \Nwere able to come this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we saw your name listed as a Tezuka prize finalist
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at a convenience store\N back in middle school,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.91,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,650)}we made you our rival and\N pledged to overtake you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to stop \N{\i1}Tanto{\i0} and aim higher
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because you were there\N as our rival, Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.30,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi and I are fated rivals.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eternal rivals."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be written as "formidable \Nenemy" but pronounced as "friend."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to put everything we've learned into this one,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll win for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have confidence in it, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall return to work.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A rival, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting all tense now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.66,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put the complicated stuff on hold for now and get to celebrating!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro gets the piece\N with the chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.68,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Azuki's homemade cake!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.09,0:05:32.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,They're both really happy with being serialized in Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's inside...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A USB stick?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.69,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho prepared this kind of surprise?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Akito, bring your \Ncomputer over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is it alright for the\N two of us to see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit embarrassing,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.60,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it's fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.66,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, your birthday \Npresent made me really happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I received a drawing from Mashiro, the mangaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a vocal \Npresent, as a voice actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just her voice?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a video letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, Kaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she gotten better at singing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, she did say she was\N going to learn how to sing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's been an editor change?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.59,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The Chief Editor noticed, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can I have a moment?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you do something \Nyou need to apologize for?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I submitted it as if it was all my work,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had Hattori help me...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.94,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve to be removed from it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a bad thing to \Nreceive the advice of others.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that is only if you are willing\N to cast aside your pride
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.96,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and listen carefully to the \Nperson offering advice.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.08,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This serialization is a result of you taking action to help Ashirogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could tell that Hattori \Nplayed a large part in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And he also understands Ashirogi well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided \Nto leave them to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.90,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I suppose it's time \Nfor you to return the favor.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's \Nhaving some troubles.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.03,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting a new editor?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we just got serialized...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you should be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting Hattori back?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miura, you've \Ndone so much for us,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and we finally got this far together...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's okay to be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.56,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is frustrating to get a \Ndifferent assignment now,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.52,0:09:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but it worked out so that Hattori and I have swapped places.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in charge of {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Make {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0} \Na big hit with Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll duke it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We definitely won't lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To you or to Niizuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Akina Aiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose, either!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Shuujin, I'm going to our studio!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.76,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,How nice...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It feels like a man's world!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the long face?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for me\N to be Ashirogi's editor?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I did all that...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it seems selfish, \Nand I feel bad about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.97,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,But really,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.25,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi overcame some huge obstacles.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.04,0:10:53.50,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I hope Fukuda understands this
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.38,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and doesn't get any crazy ideas...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.38,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose, either!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.67,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take a \Nbreak, at least for today?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lets head over to Ashirogi's now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.12,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been waiting\N for you all this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the earlier the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone from kids to housewives are snatching up Otter figures!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I did hear some rumors about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, it's time for \N"This week's Aoki Ko!"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki wants...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Otter figure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An Otter figure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll sign one of each kind and give them all to her personally!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to give it to her editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the {\i1}Otters{\i0}\N anime is doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked my editor about this, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.86,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about that\N "secret" Otter figure?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can exchange the \Nhands with real limestone!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant really wants it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your assistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats on your serialization!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, I'm glad to be\N working with you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to look over it again, starting with chapter one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the first chapter\N can get first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It got serialized
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.64,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because they judged it could win\N over Niizuma's manga, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they took a vote on whether\N this manga could win
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,over {\i1}Crow{\i0} and {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The result was 4 vs. 3 for Lose.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.31,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's plenty of potential for you to win from here on out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it got serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,4 vs. 3 for lose...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be enough to\N just look it over again.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.20,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to rewrite it so anyone can agree that we'll win!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough \Ntime to rewrite it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it work.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.46,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Putting this zeal into their manga...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need battles after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crow{\i0} may have battles,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0} has \Nstorylines that don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.31,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, where do you\N think we're losing to Eiji?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to say,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be his expressiveness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he uses perspective
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and sound effects.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings and portrayal of the \Ncharacters are straight and full-bodied,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and his dialogue is polished \Nand easy to understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets inside the characters.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, you \Nbeat him in your sketching.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro's realistic art \Nis better than his.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the sheer \Namount of Takagi's ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the novel \Nversion of {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0} on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm their editor now, \NI carry a copy with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show it to us?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She wrote it herself?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at Akina's urging,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be made available\N soon after the new year.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the content is pretty much the same as the manuscripts Niizuma received.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He cuts out the unneeded\N parts in the manuscript...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.08,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and inserts new scenes as necessary.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you compare the two,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that Niizuma's expressiveness
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,made {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0} much better.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done so much with it,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say this is more about his imagination than his expression.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagination, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the way he uses the\N space in his panel layouts...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Panels with no dialogue.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Panels with nothing but scenery.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Panels where he zooms out and shows the whole picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent closeups of characters.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Readers can freely give \Nit their own interpretation.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It engages their imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this because I don't put \Nblank panels in my names?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I put them in myself later,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're few and far between.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You both need to consider \Nyour panel choices more carefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.96,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Hattori...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We jumped straight into a meeting without officially handing it over...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't mind that at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even \Nproperly thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you've done.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work together in the future,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,please take care of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try hard too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could come here right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my doubts are gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take what you've \Ndone with {\i1}+NATURAL
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and use that popularity\N to my advantage.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bring it on!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.88,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Jumping straight into such \Nan advanced meeting...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.32,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,they're amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.20,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,To reach their level soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.04,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Miura, you\N can take it from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's start our meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only for work,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nice to be meeting \Nwith such a pretty girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you say\N something like that,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sue you for sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't sue me...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori cast me aside...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't fall in love anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the best \Nauthor in the business!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The best!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}you{\i0} are my editor!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better act like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.34,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Mom, I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Can I really do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't look at them!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawings that get you\N inside the characters, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting in blank spaces \Nand sound effects too...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that hard?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.52,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much we revise, \NI don't think we can beat Eiji's sense for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,If I can let my \Nimagination flow like Eiji's...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.62,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and express Shuujin's names better...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Hattori.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think you'll\N have the name done by?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, aren't you on vacation?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Until January 6th, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.95,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're rewriting your name, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to take it easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come see it when you're done.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe not on New Year's day.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're making you go along with our schedule.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori is a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about on the 2nd?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to redo 52 pages?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we'll get it done!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you after\N noon on the 2nd.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Miura, the editor who will be taking over {\i1}+NATURAL{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Miura Goro.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.84,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were \NAshirogi's editor, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.76,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have made them write a cliché gag manga!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi's all about realistic\N stories with realistic art!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one they're doing is like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits them perfectly!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job on getting them there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.99,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around, Ashirogi \Nwill be a tough opponent.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With a manga that can compete with mine: {\i1}Perfect Crime Club{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it has serious humor\N along with serious art.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.01,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,And the protagonist must be someone just like Takagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.16,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,And they'll do this...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.81,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,and that!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, did you tell him what it was about?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't tell him anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have ESP.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.52,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Akina and Niizuma...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.52,0:20:17.44,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,With them as my \Npartners, I'll definitely grow!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.78,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work hard so that \Nwe don't lose to Ashirogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.24,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Imagination...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,blank spaces...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,and sound effects.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It probably comes to Eiji naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Like how he turns \Na script into a manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.21,0:20:43.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Shuujin's script shouldn't\N be any worse than Iwase's!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Takagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mashiro's saying\N some weird stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come over and \Ntalk to him, if you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.44,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird stuff?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying he wants the \Nstory in script-only format!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Script only?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know \Nhow to do paneling now...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a step backwards?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With just a script, I \Ncan use my imagination!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.09,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feel constrained by the name.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.80,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}I'd rather just be given a script \Nso that I can draw freely!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put the blank\N panels where I want!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if Takagi's okay \Nwith it, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say for sure if \Nthat'll make it better.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe doing it that way
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,will give me more time to write out details on the characters' emotions.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hattori?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.99,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.74,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What was I worried about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.74,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,We do work well together, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.21,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,They're relying on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.62,0:21:58.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I can aim for the top with them!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.79,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I started drawing a new one-shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.84,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0}'s rating is below \NMaster Niizuma and Hiramaru's,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,, and just about even with Aoki's.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let Ashirogi pass me too,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we won't be the \N"Fukuda Team" any more!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.06,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still aim higher!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this one-shot \Naffects your serialization...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.19,0:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I won't let {\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0} slip!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, that would be...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.70,0:22:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write this 45 page one shot while continuing with {\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0} as usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.12,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw straight through the New Year's holiday without a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. If you're this determined,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll support you.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.92,0:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Ashirogi Muto!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.97,0:24:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our serialization finally begins!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely beat Niizuma Eiji!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.64,0:24:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Fukuda's one-shot?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.64,0:24:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Votes and Charts.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.06,0:24:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,An inherited dream can\N become even bigger!
